-. COMPILE

    Required libraries are:
	glib/gtk+ 2.24 or later
	util (or gnomesupport) library

    Compile and Install:
	./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr/local
	make
	sudo make install

    Run:
	/usr/local/bin/gtkcomm

    If you run the gtkcomm first time, ~/.gtkcomm directory is created.  You
    may want to check all the files in that directory to tune the gtkcomm.

